text: Parves-et-Nattages is a commune in the Ain department of east France, in the Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes region. The municipality started on January 1, 2016. The two old communes Parves and Nattages to make the new commune.Arrêté préfectoral 24 December 2015 ==Related pages== *Communes of the Ain department ==References== Category:2016 establishments in France
title: Parves-et-Nattages
